Malky Mackay has been sacked by Wigan Athletic after just five months in charge . 
  The Latics lost 2-0 to Derby County on Monday night . 
  Mackay is facing an FA investigation into a series of text messages he sent . 
  The Cardiff City boss was sacked by Cardiff in November . 
  Wigan are facing relegation after a poor run of form . 
  Gary Caldwell is expected to take over as caretaker manager . 
 